    ns2:comment """comments: This one is a bit weird. The inchikey in our db directs me here: https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/6484 but if I then search for 	
Dibutyl-stannane then I go to this pubchem reference https://pubchem.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/compound/Dibutylstannane. So, which one is the correct one?""";
    rdfs:label "Dibutyltin", "Dibutyltin"@nl-be;
